com.nitrous.gwt.earth.client.demo.draw
Class CircleHandler

java.lang.Object
  com.nitrous.gwt.earth.client.demo.draw.CircleHandler
All Implemented Interfaces:
MouseClickListener, MouseListener, MouseMoveListener, DrawingHandler
public class CircleHandler
extends java.lang.Object

This handler registers a mouse listener that can be used to drawn circles on Google Earth Based upon formulas found here: http://www.barnabu.co.uk/geapi/polyplot/

Author:
Nick
